{"tid":338100,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"過左今日(28) 我要重新追翻我女朋友","createTime":"2017-07-28T01:27:37.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-03T07:06:20.000Z","uid":56052,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d3958ca1d66adcef92e4deec383cc475f31f541b","tid":338100,"uid":56052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T01:27:37.000Z","msg":"拍左差唔多兩年拖，好多問題都一直係到逃避<br />\n直到最近終於為呢啲內在因素，我地決定分開下，而今日做埋最後一日情侶<br />\n我發現自己一直以來都唔夠了解呢個咁好嘅女仔，我知道再多嘅道歉同眼淚已經彌補唔到<br />\n儘管佢再愛對方，都已經攰<br />\n<br />\n所以過左今日，28號，我要重新追過佢<br />\n<br />\n（我想借呢個平台嚟做樹窿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 希望路過嘅巴絲可以入嚟為我打打下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不勝感激）"},{"pid":"1d93207701cb60c6b1982becfff9f76b00c63ca5","tid":338100,"uid":56052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T01:31:09.000Z","msg":"day 0<br />\n去同佢一齊翻工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n希望今日過得開開心心<br />\n留翻個最後嘅美好回憶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"acb2f0059137a3e1e20616ac80a1c94df7ebda12","tid":338100,"uid":59569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T01:31:45.000Z","msg":"加油"},{"pid":"4283616e2f03fc39c65b0e284e2d39b35a5606ee","tid":338100,"uid":56052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T01:35:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>加油</blockquote><br />\n多謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d3b04f1730b2b6ec9dcf90fa7a40fa1bb8ea87d","tid":338100,"uid":20217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T01:43:03.000Z","msg":"巴打加油<br />\n祝你成功<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42529d916ece7d25832da80bf3d36caeb74ad1db","tid":338100,"uid":56052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T04:03:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>巴打加油<br />\n祝你成功<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" 